qas.question: Patriarch cardinals are not given what title?

plausible_answers.text: be part of the episcopal order

qas.question: What did Pope Paul VI decree in 1965 about the patriarchs of the Western Catholic Churches?

plausible_answers.text: patriarchs of the Eastern Catholic Churches
